    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Golemworks》</strong>是一款融合了塔防与工厂建造元素的实验性游戏。你需要搭建一座能够量产自律机械大军的工厂。这些自律机械会自动投入战斗，抵御一波接一波逼近的暗影，保卫你的魔像铸造厂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308140/extras/12cc25cd3aa2d9b4edf2a9f0ff9c1e92.poster.avif?t=1772140662\" width=708 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308140/extras/12cc25cd3aa2d9b4edf2a9f0ff9c1e92.webm?t=1772140662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308140/extras/12cc25cd3aa2d9b4edf2a9f0ff9c1e92.mp4?t=1772140662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >模具会随着冷却时间循环激活，并生成魔像核心，即自律机械的“配方”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308140/extras/edd53dd2adf5d28bdadc614d27d17887.poster.avif?t=1772140662\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308140/extras/edd53dd2adf5d28bdadc614d27d17887.webm?t=1772140662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308140/extras/edd53dd2adf5d28bdadc614d27d17887.mp4?t=1772140662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >催化剂是生产的基础设施。它们可以为核心提升等级、附加元素属性，或进行其他方面的改造</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308140/extras/90b0851daf09921c2eb46c90d92c6528.poster.avif?t=1772140662\" width=592 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308140/extras/90b0851daf09921c2eb46c90d92c6528.webm?t=1772140662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308140/extras/90b0851daf09921c2eb46c90d92c6528.mp4?t=1772140662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能否在危机中幸存，全看你如何优化魔像大军的战斗力。祝你好运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可解锁的催化剂</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种挑战与不同难度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽模式</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内所有美术均使用Aseprite纯手工绘制。商店封面图由@afique_asyraf绘制。</p>",
